### Get all candidates
GET {{url}}/candidates
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Get candidate by ID
GET {{url}}/candidates/2
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Create new candidate
POST {{url}}/candidates
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Holger Troels",
  "phone": "71700749",
  "educationBackground": "Computer Science"
}

### Update candidate
PUT {{url}}/candidates/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Mia Updated",
  "phone": "87651234",
  "educationBackground": "Bachelor in Software Engineering"
}

### Link skill til candidate
PUT {{url}}/candidates/1/skills/2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Filter by skill category
GET {{url}}/candidates?category=PROG_LANG
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Report: top by popularity
GET {{url}}/reports/candidates/top-by-popularity
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}